courseMetadata.youwilllearn:
Ammon predicts the future of braids: detailed and tight (think the Kardashians’ boxer braids), not the fluffy, pieced-out braids we’ve been seeing.
Matt gives us the deets on creating the perfect pony. Here’s a couple secrets: Backcomb your base, tilt her head back before tying the pony (to let gravity help, not harm, your work) and use elastic thread, not an elastic band, for more tightness
Leah drops the color knowledge with tips for how-to color curls + make your melts even meltier.
